What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Two Wheeler Crash Guard Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Two Wheeler Crash Guard Market

The two-wheeler crash guard market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 5.85% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on two wheeler crash guard market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The rise in the sales of vehicles globally is escalating the growth of two wheeler crash guard market.

Two wheeler crash guard refers to a kind of accessory utilized to protect the vehicle body components along with parts at the time of decline when it is parked or in its reduced speed. At the time of two-wheeler collisions, the crash guard avoids the plastic and fiber body parts and components. The product is made up of mild steel and also stainless steel due to the high toughness of the materials providing lengthy functional life.

The rise in the two wheeler manufacturing across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of two wheeler crash guard market. The rise in the development of the two wheeler vehicles by the manufacturers owning to the increasing concerns regarding safety of the passenger and presence of stringent regulation by the government on the manufacturing of two wheelers accelerate the market growth. The increase in demand for motorcycles as well as its aftermarket accessories because of the rise in consumer inclination towards leisure activities associated with conventional motorcycles and scooters, such as bike stunts, off-road activities, and racing, and surge in the number of collisions and accidents further influence the market. Additionally, expansion of the automotive sector, favorable regulations, urbanization, high in disposable income, an increase in development activities positively affect the two wheeler crash guard market. Furthermore, developments in the crash guards extend profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, concerns regarding weight and poorly made materials are expected to obstruct the market growth. The negative impact of COVID-19 on the automotive manufacturing is projected to challenge the two wheeler crash guard market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

